OL,6,GThere have been a few technical
OL,7,Ggremlins with the cameras in BBC News'
OL,8,GStudio B in recent weeks.
OL,10,FWe've perhaps become accustomed to
OL,11,Fseeing the automated cameras in Studio
OL,12,FE going walkies over the years. Such
OL,13,Fincidents are still rare in Studio B.
OL,15,FBut tonight was one of those rare
OL,16,Fexceptions. At the start of the weather
OL,17,Fsegment on the BBC News at Ten, the
OL,18,Fcamera started to swing around.
OL,3,CCamera mishap during the BBC News at
